White Paper: PanjoCoin (PNJC)              
“Laughter heals. PNJC empowers.” A Decentralized Charity Protocol on Polygon 


Chapter 1: Introduction & Mission
1.1 A New Era of Social Responsibility
By 2026, the cryptocurrency market demands real utility and tangible impact.
PanjoCoin (PNJC) is a utility-driven meme token designed to address a fundamental issue: the lack of transparency and efficiency in funding social initiatives.
We combine the viral nature of meme culture with the transparency of blockchain technology to support real-world humanitarian causes.
1.2 Our Mission
To establish sustainable and transparent funding for the ClownCare medical clowning program operated by the Smiledonate Foundation in Tbilisi.
We believe Web3 technologies can transform charity from one-time donations into a self-sustaining economic ecosystem.
